data.description: Possible FHA assumable loan at amazing interest rate for qualified buyers. Like NEW construction under $225k.  Amazing, fully renovated, move-in ready home! Home has been completely made new (again) over the past year including new foundation, roof and shingles, new plumbing, new electrical. Updated living space with Bamboo flooring, fresh paint, and modern updated fixtures throughout. Open living and dining room creating a wonderful entertaining space. Beautiful granite counter-tops, stainless steel appliances, and more than ample cabinet space. Wonderful laundry room for more storage. Refrigerator,  washer and dryer convey with the home. Imagine an acre with a huge, fenced-in backyard and no HOA fees.  Privacy and freedom in your new home. Approximately 35 mins to downtown Raleigh. One mile off of I-95.  15 mins to Campbell University.
